{
  "doc_id": "7452",
  "text": "Demographic measures included age, sex, race, ethnicity, and annual income. Comborbid medical conditions were determined based on self-report of prior physician diagnosis. Physical performance was assessed with the Senior Fitness Test, [CITATION_1] which includes the following standard measures: chair stand, arm curl, 2-minute step, sit and reach, back scratch, and 8-foot up-and-go tests.",
