      "title": "Senior Fitness Test Manual",
      "abstract": "Fitness testing in later years - recognizing the unique needs of older adults the senior fitness test - defining functional fitness parameters test validity, reliability, and performance standards - identifying relevant fitness measures for older adults test administration - establishing consistent testing protocols test results - interpreting and using feedback to motivate and improve performance."
